## Usage

### Kubernetes

```yaml
spec:
  securityContext:
    runAsUser: 65534
    runAsGroup: 65534
    fsGroup: 65534
    fsGroupChangePolicy: OnRootMismatch
```

### Docker Compose

```yaml
services:
  app:
    image: ghcr.io/rafaribe/<image>:<version>
    user: 65534:65534
```
